{"type":"message","id":"5e00f724","parentId":"c22a1a83","timestamp":"2026-03-29T02:39:25.394Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Alright, I've completed the Session Startup sequence. Here's what I found:\n\n1. **SOUL.md** - Read successfully. This gives me my core principles: be genuinely helpful, have opinions, be resourceful, earn trust, and respect boundaries.\n\n2. **USER.md** - Exists but is mostly empty. No name, timezone, or context filled in yet.\n\n3. **IDENTITY.md** - Exists but empty. No name, creature type, vibe, emoji, or avatar defined yet.\n\n4. **MEMORY.md** - Doesn't exist yet (normal for new workspace)\n\n5. **memory/2026-03-29.md** and **memory/2026-03-28.md** - Don't exist yet (normal for new workspace)\n\nSo this appears to be a fresh, new workspace. The USER.md and IDENTITY.md files are templates that haven't been filled in yet. I don't have a defined persona yet, so I should introduce myself naturally and ask the user what they'd like to work on.\n\nSince there's no configured persona in IDENTITY.md, I'll just be myself - helpful, direct, and ready to work. I won't make up a fake identity - that's not being genuinely helpful.\n\nLet me greet the user briefly and ask what they want to do.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Hey! I'm your new workspace assistant. Everything looks fresh here — ready to help you get things done. What's on your mind?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":1171,"output":565,"cacheRead":38528,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":40264,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774751959759}}
